behavior place_coffee_maker_on_surface(coffee_maker:item, surface:item):

        achieve on(coffee_maker, surface)
        # Place the coffee maker on the stable surface

        achieve plugged(coffee_maker)
        # Plug in the coffee maker to the power socket
